It 's just that with the fashion for things Japanese , Maneki Nekos prevail , and <COREF ID="49" TYPE="IDENT">figures of three - legged toads</COREF> are not nearly as prevalent as <COREF ID="49" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> once were .
